

Parallel computing 이란?

Necessary:
    => mainly because of memory 

    메모리 문제로 인해 대용량 분산처리 
    => also for processing power 

how it works:
    => split tasks up into several smllaer subtasks 
        데이터 처리를 분산한다 

    => Distribute these subtasks over several computer 
        데이터 처리를 여러 컴퓨터에 분산한다 

    => 그래서 데이터 처리를 아주 효율적으로 
    빠르게 처리한다 


Benefits and risks of parallel computing 

- Employees = processing units 

- Advantages:
    => Extra processing power 
    => Rduced memory footprint

- Disadvantages:
    => moving data incurs a cost 
    => Communication time( consume to merge)